    "description": "在这个瞬息万变的3V3踢球格斗游戏中，把对手从赛场上打飞并进球得分。您可以选择15位以上风格各异的斗士，通过弹射史莱姆，抛掷豆腐，用火箭助推来取得胜利。和好友组队，技压对手，成为Omega级的斗士吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869590/extras/27e364c9ea209f27d880bef836141b77.poster.avif?t=1758746829\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869590/extras/27e364c9ea209f27d880bef836141b77.webm?t=1758746829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869590/extras/27e364c9ea209f27d880bef836141b77.mp4?t=1758746829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><strong>每一局都有截然不同体验</strong><br>爆轰、弹射、用蛮力冲锋把对手撞进灼热或带电的地图陷阱里。在鬼村地图里用风驰电掣的速度冲刺，并避开阿特拉斯实验室的重力陷阱旋涡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869590/extras/6f7c649a1b5251c41a6217827501b871.poster.avif?t=1758746829\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869590/extras/6f7c649a1b5251c41a6217827501b871.webm?t=1758746829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869590/extras/6f7c649a1b5251c41a6217827501b871.mp4?t=1758746829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><strong>玩出自己的风格</strong><br>赚取分数，解锁强力的新斗士，每一位都有独特的技能。通过流派技，创造你自己定制的游戏风格，还可以通过皮肤和表情包改变外观。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869590/extras/45d6e3fd88601a7107da3e00eed5daf0.poster.avif?t=1758746829\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869590/extras/45d6e3fd88601a7107da3e00eed5daf0.webm?t=1758746829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869590/extras/45d6e3fd88601a7107da3e00eed5daf0.mp4?t=1758746829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><strong>大型赛季更新</strong><br>《Omega Strikers》每个赛季都会持续迭代，增加新的赛场地图、新的可解锁内容，以及更多的游戏方式。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869590/extras/14b08bb18c55ec18482ec06db11fa32e.poster.avif?t=1758746829\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869590/extras/14b08bb18c55ec18482ec06db11fa32e.webm?t=1758746829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869590/extras/14b08bb18c55ec18482ec06db11fa32e.mp4?t=1758746829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>展示的内容可能需要从游戏内商店单独购买，且限时限量发售。本游戏包含游戏内购买。",
